"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"üê• gm hatchlings!!\\n\\nToday‚Äôs guide will be covering the [Avalanche network](https://www.avax.network/), and how to setup and bridge your Ethereum (ETH) over to AVAX - the network‚Äôs native coin used for transactions on the network!\\n\\nSetting up your wallet and bridging (converting one network‚Äôs currency to another) can be daunting, but fear not! Grab a **desktop/laptop**, a snack, and follow our bushy tail down the rabbithole: we shall guide you! üêáüï≥\\n\\n> **Be sure to check out the prerequisite tutorials to get setup first**\\n\\n* [How to set up MetaMask Wallet](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/-UWjheu5bsRvMUa78_O242czkl5AwHs58jT9S-p-0u0)\\n\\nBefore diving in, lets learn a little more about the Avalanche network, and why it exists!\\n\\n### ü§î What is Avalanche (AVAX)?\\n\\nAvalanche is blockchain platform that focuses on blazing fast transaction speeds, super low transaction fees, and being eco-friendly by being able to process thousands of transactions per second!\\n\\nFor comparison, transacting on the Ethereum blockchain can be costly, and the network can only process around 15-45 transactions per second.\\n\\nAvalanche, and many other Layer 2 networks work to lower transaction fees and drastically increase the number of transactions that can be made per second making it cheaper and faster to use!\\n\\nüêáüï≥ To dive deeper and learn more about the difference between Layer 1 and Layer 2 networks visit here.\\n\\n### ü§© Wow! How Do I Set Up My Wallet?\\n\\nPurchasing AVAX lets you use it to transact on their network, and interact with the many decentralized apps (dapps) on Avalanche.\\n\\nFirst make sure you have a MetaMask account, visit our tutorial [here](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/-UWjheu5bsRvMUa78_O242czkl5AwHs58jT9S-p-0u0) to help get set up!\\n\\n1. Go into your MetaMask wallet and click the **Ethereum Mainnet dropdown** button at the top to open the Network Menu\\n   1. You can use this menu to switch between networks (Ethereum & Avalanche)\\n2. Click **Add Network** at the bottom\\n3. You will be prompted with this screen asking you enter a few details\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F4kTK5BN5f_rkrhQf1x5pX.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nTo add Avalanche as a network, copy and paste the details below into the boxes or copy and paste them directly from Avalanche‚Äôs website [here](https://support.avax.network/en/articles/4626956-how-do-i-set-up-metamask-on-avalanche).\\n\\n* **Network Name**: Avalanche Network\\n* **New RPC URL**: <https://api.avax.network/ext/bc/C/rpc>\\n* **ChainID**: 43114\\n* **Symbol**: AVAX\\n* **Explorer**: <https://snowtrace.io/>\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FdJiKp-uW2Pp8H5_3jwi9S.png&w=2048&q=90)\\n\\nOnce you have copied and pasted the information into the boxes below click save to add the network.\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FdEQuEanD-Fs8f_o-t1B1d.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nüêáüï≥ Alternatively, you can also visit [chainlist.org](https://chainlist.org), search for Avalanche Mainnet, and connect you wallet to automatically add it as a network! \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/cLia8PQja7_OendFDCps9.png?height=1462&width=2824)\\n\\nYou should get a confirmation message in the bottom right of the MetaMask website, and you should now be able to switch to the Avalanche Network in the Network Menu.\\n\\nüéä Congratulations!! You have added the Avalanche Network to your wallet!\\n\\n### üíÉ Sweet! Now How do I get AVAX?\\n\\n1. First things first, you want to make sure you have some Ethereum in your wallet\\n2. Next, we are going to want to wrap our ETH for wETH (a cross-platform token that represents ETH‚Äôs value exactly)\\n   1. üêáüï≥ wETH (Wrapped Ethereum) is a ERC-20 token representing ETH 1:1 that allows for more functionality across platforms that handle ERC-20 tokens like Avalanche.\\n      1. To read more about wETH, and why it exists visit their website [here](https://weth.io/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Toeipo_xJo_b8T4O_evI2.png?height=1644&width=2688)\\n\\n1. Go to your MetaMask wallet, and click the **Swap button** to the right\\n2. Under **Swap to**, click the dropdown and type wETH\\n3. Select **WETH**\\n   1. ***Note***\\\\*:\\\\* *Make sure it says Verified on x number of sources. This means MetaMask has verified that the token you are swapping to is legit!*\\n4. Enter the amount of ETH you would like to swap, and click **Review Swap** to open the confirmation menu\\n5. Click **Swap** to confirm\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Uf4pgYuizNjXtRcBUB-LG.png?height=670&width=1708&&size=medium)\\n\\n### üòé Nice! You have wrapped ETH into wETH!\\n\\nYou should see your wETH balance under Assets!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XYb0HVTU6dM3Jc8pbzNHo.png?height=522&width=1030)\\n\\n### üåÅ How to bridge wETH to AVAX\\n\\nOkay, now that we have some wETH, it‚Äôs time to bridge it into AVAX!\\n\\n1. Visit <https://bridge.avax.network/>, the official Avalanche Bridge\\n2. Next, connect your MetaMask to the dapp\\n3. Once connected, click on the dropdown next to **1INCH**\\n4. Type wETH and click WETH from the list (you should see your wETH balance)\\n5. Enter how much wETH you would like to bridge to AVAX and click **Transfer**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/KHBe8I0L2HrtJBNUi-Iiq.png?height=678&width=1746&&size=medium)\\n\\nA **Transaction Status** screen will open, showing you the progress of your bridge\\n\\n* ***Note:*** *The Ethereum transaction should take around 10-15 minutes, while the Avalanche transaction should only take a few seconds*\\n  * *To learn more, visit the official Avalanche Bridge FAQ page [here](https://docs.avax.network/learn/avalanche-bridge-faq/)*\\n\\n![https://medium.com/stakingbits/how-to-bridge-tokens-onto-avalanche-7307aa0fb930](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Q9aQ5TCzlKgl151u4gKD6.png?height=452&width=890)\\n\\n### üíÉ Yay!! You have officially converted your ETH to AVAX!\\n\\nYou can now use it to interact with the Avalanche network and its various dapps!\\n\\nTo view your AVAX balance:\\n\\n1. Go back to your MetaMask wallet\\n2. Click the Ethereum Mainnet dropdown to switch networks\\n3. You should see your AVAX balance!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/sGHSbnDOtghn9CPwGKpZU.png?height=824&width=1806)\\n\\nThat‚Äôs it folks!! I hope you enjoyed this guide down the Avalanche rabbithole!\\n\\nPlease be sure to check out our Mirror articles and follow us on Twitter for all things crypto and web3.\\n\\n[https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/rabbithole_gg](https://twitter.com/rabbithole_gg)\\n\\nüíï Stay curious frens!\",\"timestamp\":1640185715,\"title\":\"Tutorial: How to Setup & Bridge Funds to Avalanche (AVAX)\",\"publication\":\"rabbithole\"},\"digest\":\"wZotRSEcsgB8yk0aG8rJjZouYzvZsPylX5M5ECMMYxM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x75A548a2Df9Ba12af496BD5364F642C9cE3C3976\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eKUlBLd_oUFUSo7a9O6fO-UcefvbvTKIDodn6cfer3E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"OXIaur0YsjtTsE6aX9W2kCpYF0tL6AqPK7mbmTHqupQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"lmo39dE2490TA76PENmAetpeEe1fPA0oSg2PQAXjalCl1IoGaoGWcO_hKLfzdkUBBNi0fdtXdrgDuhd9v23RSw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x51271ff6c4d655f8e32f3306b478fe7d375dd8408b0163dd06467a952d2a93307b2bf840465eb502cc572261c0f72b74ac9ba166418b61a0ca1909a81fb8655f1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eKUlBLd_oUFUSo7a9O6fO-UcefvbvTKIDodn6cfer3E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"OXIaur0YsjtTsE6aX9W2kCpYF0tL6AqPK7mbmTHqupQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"wZotRSEcsgB8yk0aG8rJjZouYzvZsPylX5M5ECMMYxM\"}"